content:
What are some idiomatic expressions that can be used to convey the idea of standing still? Here are some options from a table of idioms:
const idioms = {
   "idioms":[
      {
         "expression":"Standing still like a statue",
         "meaning":"Not moving at all"
      },
      {
         "expression":"Frozen in place",
         "meaning":"Unable to move or act"
      },
      {
         "expression":"Like a deer in headlights",
         "meaning":"Stunned or surprised, unable to react"
      },
      {
         "expression":"Glued to the spot",
         "meaning":"Unable to move or leave"
      },
      {
         "expression":"Dead in the water",
         "meaning":"Not progressing or moving forward"
      }
   ]
};
